title: Is the ‘Umbrella Corporation’ Logo Oddly Similar to a Wuhan Biotech Lab’s?
subtitle: Some concern arose over apparent connections between the video game "Resident Evil" and a new coronavirus outbreak.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: The fictional "Umbrella Corporation" from the game "Resident Evil" shares a logo with a biotech lab in Wuhan, Hubei Province in China, where a new coronavirus is believed to have originated.
